				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">This article is about the pre-Columbian Maya civilization.  For a discussion of the modern Maya, see <a href="Maya_peoples" title="Maya peoples">Maya peoples</a>.  For other meanings of the word Maya, see <a href="Maya_(disambiguation)" title="Maya (disambiguation)" class="mw-redirect">Maya</a>.</div>
